7/12/12/nikos-kazantzakis-and-thought-leadership/ \"Nikos Kazantzakis and thought leadership\"], 2013.\n* Ioannis G. Zaglaris, \"Nikos Kazantzakis - end of time due to copyright\", [https://www.pdf-archive.com/2017/12/12/gisap-educational-sciences/ ''GISAP: Educational Sciences'', 4, pp. 53-54], 2014\n* Ioannis G. Zaglaris, [http://www.pdf-archive.com/2016/01/14/challenge-in-writing1/ \"Challenge in Writing\", 2015]\n\n==External links==\n{{Commons category}}\n{{Wikiquote}}\n*[https://web.archive.org/web/20070224115200/http://www.kazantzakis-museum.gr/index.php The Nikos Kazantzakis Museum, Crete]\n*[http://www.historical-museum.gr/kazantzakis/index1.html The Nikos Kazantzakis Pages at the Historical Museum of Crete]\n*[http://www.tehrantimes.com/index_View.asp?code=165972 Iran to pay homage to Greek author Kazantzakis \u2013 ''Tehran Times'', 10 April 2008]\n*[https://web.archive.org/web/20081016100133/http://www.amis-kazantzaki.gr/ Society of Nikos Kazantzakis friends] {{in lang|el}}\n*[http://www.kazantzakispublications.org/ Kazantzakis Publications (Patroclos Stavrou)]\n* {{LCAuth|n79100889|Nikos Kazantzakis|128|ue}}\n\n{{Nikos Kazantzakis}}\n{{Authority control}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Kazantzakis, Nikos}}\n[[Category:Nikos Kazantzakis| ]]\n[[Category:1883 births]]\n[[Category:1957 deaths]]\n[[Category:20th-century dramatists and playwrights]]\n[[Category:20th-century Greek philosophers]]\n[[Category:20th-century Greek poets]]\n[[Category:20th-century Greek novelists]]\n[[Category:People from Heraklion]]\n[[Category:People from Ottoman Crete]]\n[[Category:Greeks of the Ottoman Empire]]\n[[Category:Theatre in Greece]]\n[[Category:Greek nationalists]]\n[[Category:20th-century Greek dramatists and playwrights]]\n[[Category:Greek atheists]] \n[[Category:Greek writers]]\n[[Category:Cretan novelists]]\n[[Category:Greek journalists]]\n[[Category:Greek travel writers]]\n[[Category:Greek speculative fiction writers]]\n[[Category:National and Kapodistrian University of Athens 